IClassMobile
============

This project is a mobile .NET MAUI adaptation based on ideas and API/WebVPN
workflow references from the open source project:

  iclass_buaa
  https://github.com/zeroduhyy/iclass_buaa

The upstream project is licensed under the MIT License. Its copyright and
permission notice are preserved in LICENSE.

Changes in this repository include a mobile UI, .NET MAUI project structure,
Android packaging, direct iClass calendar/sign-in workflow, WebVPN URL wrapping
and login flow adaptation, update checking, and mobile release packaging.
